data.description:
Charming, clean and well maintained home that is close to the lake. Bathrooms and kitchen were recently updated as well as the flooring. 
There is also a separate storage building, screened in porch and covered carport. The roof and air conditioning were both recently replaced.
NO neighbors on either side! This is a warm home with very spacious surroundings. You can enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage from one of two porches in a very peaceful setting. There is a boat dock and picnic area only one block away!
